00:03:37.560 --> 00:03:39.240
It has a y-intercept
at negative 2.

00:03:39.240 --> 00:03:40.010
So negative 2.

00:03:40.010 --> 00:03:44.560
So 1, 2, at negative 2,
and has a slope of 1/2.

00:03:44.560 --> 00:03:47.150
So that means that for
